    • Constructor Detail

      • TileLoaderWorker

        public TileLoaderWorker(TileQuery subQuery,
                javax.media.opengl.GLProfile profile,
                Cache<TileResource> cache)
        Each TileLoaderWorker is instantiated with a "task". This task in form of a Query object or a extended object of Query is passed as a parameter. The TileLoaderWorker will work on this query. After its work is done, the results are stored and the TileLoaderWorker dies.
        Parameters:
        subQuery - The query this TileLoaderWorker has to perform.
        profile - The OpenGL-profile to use when loading texture-data.
        cache - The cache to use for querying cached tiles.
